@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F1F8E9
skinparam classBorderColor #33691E
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
actor "Customer" as C
participant "Delivery Service" as DS
boundary "Seller" as S
actor "Admin" as A
S -> DS : Make Payment
A ->> S : Checkout
A ->> C : Apply Coupon
C ->> DS : Manage Inventory
activate DS
DS --> C : ACK
deactivate DS
note over DS : processing manage inventory
C -> DS : Write Review
C ->> S : Browse Products
@enduml